# Ethereum Wallet Checker

This repository contains a small Python tool to check an Ethereum wallet for:

* ETH balance
* Total number of transactions
* Total ETH volume sent and received
* ERC-20 token balances (via recent token transfer history) and ADD

> Files included in this repo (below you'll find the full contents so you can copy-paste into files):

```
eth-wallet-checker/
├─ README.md
├─ requirements.txt
├─ .env.example
├─ main.py
├─ helpers.py
└─ protocols.json
```

